# autoESDA


[![image](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/autoesda.svg)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/autoesda)
[![image](https://img.shields.io/conda/vn/conda-forge/autoesda.svg)](https://anaconda.org/conda-forge/autoesda)
